<bibRefCitation author="Ceregato" box="[1112,1363,1279,1304]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" refString="Ceregato, A., Raffi, S. &amp; Scarponi, D. (2007) The circalittoral / bathyal paleocommunities in the Middle Pliocene of Northern Italy: The case of the Korobkovia oblonga - Jupiteria concava paleocommunity type. Geobios, 40, 555 - 572. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1016 / j. geobios. 2006.08.004" type="journal article" year="2007">
Ceregato 
<emphasis box="[1228,1290,1279,1304]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="26">et al.</emphasis>
